<br />

<br />
You are right: some higher level enchanter haste spells (like SoV) have stat bonuses in addition to the haste component. For this reason, the spells &quot;stack&quot; in the sense that their icons can co-exist, but of course only the higher of the two haste components will be applied.</span></td>
